commit.message:
Make GAE OAuth proxy not the default

- Make client_id and client_secret mandatory
- Enable loopback auth mode by default
- Add command line option to specify the loopback port

Support OCaml 5

Use latest gapi-ocaml version

Fix #776

The target path of moved files was not updated correctly

Fix #756

Add an option to start a local web server for OAuth2 flow.
- oauth2_loopback: flag to start the local web server
- oauth2_loopback_port: port of the local web server [defaults to 8080]

Fix for extlib 1.7.8 compatibility

Use base64 encoding from Cryptokit instead of extlib, because extlib
1.7.8 removed module Base64. See ocaml/opam-repository#17998
